run(sql="
with cte as(
select a.orderDate,
        a.subOrderId,
        b.pogId,
        a.Channel
from `temp.attributed_Orders` a 
left join `all(agCmDump)` b
on a.subOrderId=b.subOrderId
where a.orderDate>'2023-02-22'
),

cte2 as(
select * from(
    select dmPublisherInfoId, 
            availability, 
            row_number() over(partition by dmPublisherInfoId order by timestamp desc) as rn 
    from `last30Days(dmPublisherInfo)` 
    where dpYMD>20230222)
where rn=1
)

select cte.orderDate,
        count(distinct cte.subOrderId) as subo, 
        count(distinct case when lower(cte.Channel) LIKE 'fb%' then cte.subOrderId end) as fb_subo 
from cte
    left join cte2
    on cte.pogId=cte2.dmPublisherInfoId 
    where cte2.availability = 'in stock'
group by cte.orderDate 
order by cte.orderDate
",1000)

with cte as(
select a.orderDate,
        a.subOrderId,
        b.pogId,
        a.Channel
from `temp.attributed_Orders` a 
left join `all(agCmDump)` b
on a.subOrderId=b.subOrderId
),

cte2 as(
select dmPublisherInfoId,availability from(
    select *, 
            availability, 
            row_number() over(partition by dmPublisherInfoId order by timestamp desc) as rn 
    from `last180Days(dmPublisherInfo)` 
    where TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(timestamp/1000))>'2023-02-22')
where rn=1
),

cte3 as(
select pogMarketingFeedBaseTab as pogId
        ,sum((bauNmpu-totalFixedFfcMarketingFeedBaseTab+laapFixedFfcMarketingFeedBaseTab)*pogWeightage)/sum(pogWeightage) as NM3SO
from(
    select distinct *
    from marketingFeedBaseTable
    ) a
group by pogMarketingFeedBaseTab
)

select cte.orderDate,
        count(distinct cte.subOrderId) as subo, 
        count(distinct case when lower(cte.Channel) LIKE 'fb%' then cte.subOrderId end) as fb_subo 
from cte
left join cte2
on cte.pogId=cte2.dmPublisherInfoId 
left join cte3
on cte.pogId=cte3.pogId
where cte3.NM3SO<=13
    and cte2.availability = 'in stock'
    and cte.orderDate>='2023-02-22'
group by cte.orderDate 
order by cte.orderDate desc
",1000)
